  "instructions": [
    "heat coconut oil in a large skillet over medium-high heat.",
    "add minced garlic and cook until fragrant, about 1 minute.",
    "add ground pork and cook, breaking up with a spoon, until browned and cooked through.",
    "add smoked salmon, frozen peas, and frozen spinach to the skillet.",
    "stir in fish sauce, lime juice, salt, and pepper.",
    "cook for an additional 2 minutes, until peas and spinach are tender.",
    "taste and adjust seasoning as needed.",
    "garnish with chopped cilantro and serve hot.",
